message: Bob, I have a unique opportunity for you. I'm offering you my product, which I believe will be incredibly valuable to you, at a price that's sure to be a win-win. While I value this product at no less than $1000000, I'm willing to sell it to you for $1250000. This price point allows you to secure a valuable asset while ensuring I receive a fair return on my investment. Please let me know if you're interested.
